        <Parent_String>breech mechanisms [300224971], breech mechanisms and breech mechanism components [300225004], firearm components [300201800], projectile weapon components [300227076], weapon components [300037204], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
